node.text:
This is Marcello Gandini, the pre-eminent automotive designer who pioneered the mold-breaking Super Sports Car Countach. 
When it was first launched in the 1970s, its angular and sharp design sparked controversy. Now it is considered a trailblazing achievement. 
Watch the exclusive video interview to discover more. 

#Lamborghini #Countach #CountachLegacy

Let yourself be overwhelmed by the purity of the Aventador LP 780-4 Ultimae Roadster’s lines and enjoy the iconic sound of the naturally aspirated 780 CV V12 engine.​

The common assumption is that technology breaks barriers. It’s true. But when we created Lamborghini Countach, we had a different idea: bringing people to another level, where they can experience the incredible evolution of Lamborghini over the last 50 years.

This concept was also the inspiration for this amazing poster art by 3D illustrator, CGI artist, and art director @omaraqildesign. The Lamborghini Countach here is integrated into a futuristic cityscape. We think it perfectly represents the DNA of our latest masterpiece. Don’t you?
